      "updated": 1783958445687,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTML 4 (Dynamic HTML, the DOM, etc.)\nThe browser wars were still raging - \n  HTML 5 - frameworks, libraries, etc spent a huge amount of effort to work cross browser.\n\nAngularJS - it sucks. We have rewrite this. Angular 2.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTML 4 (Dynamic HTML, the DOM, etc.)\nThe browser wars were still raging - \n  HTML 5 - frameworks, libraries, etc spent a huge amount of effort to work cross browser.\n\nAngularJS - it sucks. We have rewrite this. Angular 2.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
